@startwbs
* AgenticNativePlatform - Runtime Flow With Flux Operator And Static Cluster Roots
** 1. Flux control plane
*** Flux Operator
**** manages Flux controller lifecycle
*** FluxInstance/flux
**** sync.kind = GitRepository
**** sync.path = ./clusters/<topology>-<env>
*** GitRepository/platform
**** reads remote Git branch
*** Staged Kustomizations
**** platform-infrastructure
**** platform-secrets
**** platform-applications

** 2. North-south traffic path
*** External client
**** sends HTTP /v1 and /mcp
*** kgateway public-gateway
**** north-south entry point
**** routes traffic to agentgateway-proxy
*** agentgateway-proxy
**** protocol-aware AI gateway
**** /v1 -> litellm-upstream backend
**** /mcp -> kagent-tools-mcp-backend
*** LiteLLM
**** remote provider default path
**** optional external LM Studio path
**** optional in-cluster runtime path

** 3. Cluster components
*** platform plumbing
**** namespaces from apps/platform
**** cluster wrappers from clusters/<topology>-<env>
*** kgateway-system
**** kgateway controller
**** public-gateway
*** agentgateway-system
**** agentgateway controller
**** agentgateway-proxy
**** AgentgatewayBackend resources
**** AgentgatewayPolicy
*** kagent
**** kagent-controller
**** kagent-ui
**** kagent-tools
**** Agent: k8s-a2a-agent
**** RemoteMCPServer: kagent-tool-server
*** ai-gateway
**** LiteLLM
*** ai-models
**** tei-embeddings
**** KServe control plane
**** optional Ollama or vLLM path
*** context
**** Qdrant
**** PostgreSQL
**** Redis
*** observability
**** Prometheus
**** Grafana
**** Loki

** 4. Request and data paths
*** UI and agent path
**** kagent-ui -> kagent-controller
**** k8s-a2a-agent -> kagent-controller
**** kagent-controller -> agentgateway /v1
*** MCP path
**** RemoteMCPServer -> agentgateway /mcp/kagent-tools
**** agentgateway -> kagent-tools backend
*** LLM path
**** agentgateway -> LiteLLM
**** LiteLLM -> Gemini / OpenAI / Anthropic / Bedrock / Vertex / others
**** LiteLLM -> optional LM Studio endpoint
**** LiteLLM -> optional Ollama or vLLM path
*** Context path
**** kagent-controller -> tei-embeddings
**** kagent-controller -> Qdrant
**** kagent-controller -> PostgreSQL
**** kagent-controller -> Redis
@endwbs
